# Passenger configuration
PassengerHighPerformance on
# Pool size calculation based on:
# * memory available (scaled to account for caches)
# * max RSS megabytes per worker
PassengerMaxPoolSize <%= (@memorysize_mb * 0.70) / 250 %>
PassengerPoolIdleTime 1500
PassengerMaxRequests 2000
PassengerStatThrottleRate 120
